## Output format (all agents)

Every agent appends to the current stage file:
```markdown
---
### 🔧 Sub-agent: {id}
> Stage: {STAGE} | Triggered: {YYYY-MM-DD} | Reason: {signal}
> Inputs: {files/sections}

{agent output}

> Next: {suggested action}
---
```

